Package: scgUtils
Title: Utility functions for Sarah C Gall Ltd and associated packages
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Sarah", "Gall", , "contact@sarahcgall.co.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: scgUtils contains the utility functions for Sarah C Gall Ltd
    and the associated packages. It is primarily used for analysing polling
    results and making it easy to quickly review surveys with cross-tabs and
    data visualisations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/sarahcgall/scgUtils, https://sarahcgall.github.io/scgUtils/
